# Church Ecosystem 🌟

A decentralized, AI-powered micro-church community network built on modern Web3 stack.

## 🎯 Vision
Creating an organic ecosystem where every faith group can own their digital home, connected in a decentralized network.

## 🏗️ Architecture
- **Frontend**: Next.js/Astro + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- **Blockchain**: Solidity + Ethereum/Polygon  
- **Storage**: IPFS + Ceramic Network
- **AI**: OpenAI + LangChain + Whisper
- **Real-time**: Huddle01 + LiveKit
- **Infrastructure**: Docker + GitHub Actions

## 🚀 Quick Start
```bash
npm install
npm run devchurch-ecosystem/
├── frontend/          # Main portal & group templates
├── protocol/          # Smart contracts & subgraph
├── services/          # AI agent & sync workers  
├── definitions/       # Content schemas & templates
├── infra/            # Infrastructure as Code
└── docs/             # Documentation

**2. 创建基础定义文件**
```powershell
# 创建小组定义schema
@'
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "MicroChurch Group",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Name of the faith group"
    },
    "mission": {
      "type": "string", 
      "description": "Group'\''s mission statement"
    },
    "denomination": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["non-denominational", "baptist", "methodist", "pentecostal", "catholic", "orthodox", "other"]
    },
    "meetingFrequency": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["weekly", "bi-weekly", "monthly"]
    }
  },
